      <title>康卡斯特股价因宽带客户流失增加而暴跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-25/comcast-shares-tumble-with-growing-loss-of-broadband-customers</link>
      <description><![CDATA[有线电视巨头康卡斯特 (Comcast Corp.) 公布互联网用户流失幅度超出预期后，该公司股价周四下跌逾 7%。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-25/comcast-shares-tumble-with-growing-loss-of-broadband-customers</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 25 Apr 2024 16:17:32 GMT</pubDate>
